column5: This is starting to get old. First the van goes in then 3 sleds and I heard another fool sunk his truck by the river. http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/north/3-tourists-snowmobile-fall-through-yellowknife-lake-ice-1.4455099
Hear that someone fell in out by my old childhood neighbour Monique's floating house as well last week.
